===Etymology===
From the {{L.}} preposition ''[[trans#Latin|trans]]'' (meaning "[[across]]") + ''[[silvam]]'', the {{acc}} {{singular}} of ''[[silva]]'' meaning "[[forest]]". Meaning "across the forest".
